title: Hour 3 - Mike Florio, Jim Jackson
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Mike Florio, Jim Jackson
description:
Dan talks to Mike Florio about Washington Commanders De Jack Del Rio's comments regarding January 6th and subsequent apology. And Jim Jackson drops by to break down game 3 of the NBA Finals.
